If you’re in the market for a smartphone with great features that doesn’t break the bank, Samsung and Edgars have you covered. The Samsung Galaxy A32 LTE and A02s smartphones both offer excellent features at affordable prices. Click here to get the Samsung Galaxy A02s from Edgars. Samsung’s Galaxy A32 LTE smartphone is perfect if you want premium features at mid-range prices. The Galaxy A32 LTE boasts an octa-core processor, 4GB RAM, and 128GB storage – allowing it to store and run all of your favourite apps. It comes with a quad-lens rear camera system, too, including a 64MP primary lens that will capture your favourite moments in outstanding quality. This is complemented by a powerful 20MP front camera, which is perfect for capturing stunning selfies. These photos will look great on the A32 LTE’s 6.4-inch FHD+ Infinity-U display, which offers crisp quality, accurate colours, and a 90Hz refresh rate. All of these amazing features are powered by a massive 5,000mAh battery, which means you won’t have to worry about running out of charge. This smartphone comes in Awesome Black and Awesome Blue options, and is available from Edgars for R5,499.90 on prepaid, or for R324 per month on a 24-month contract. Another great option for those looking for the best bang for their buck is the Samsung Galaxy A02s. This smartphone boasts 3GB RAM and 32GB storage, as well as an octa-core processor. You also get an impressive triple-lens rear camera system, and a powerful 5MP front camera for all your photography needs. The 6.5-inch HD+ V Cut display is ideal for viewing your favourite videos, movies, and series, while a 5,000mAh battery keeps your smartphone running for longer. The Samsung Galaxy A02s comes in Black and Blue options, and is available for just R2,499.90 from Edgars. Click here to get this deal. If you get it on a contract, you pay just R164 per month for 24 months. View the Galaxy A32 and A02s smartphones and their specifications below. <img class="aligncenter wp-image